@startuml
title 命令与执行反馈时序
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Ground Station" as GS
participant "Protocol Runtime" as RT
participant "Vehicle Executor" as EX

GS -> RT : Command.Goto\nmessage_id = 8101\ncorrelation_id = 8101
RT --> GS : CommandResult.Received\ncorrelation_id = 8101
RT -> EX : 调度执行
EX --> RT : 语义校验通过
RT --> GS : CommandResult.Accepted\ncorrelation_id = 8101
EX --> RT : 执行中
RT --> GS : CommandResult.InProgress\nprogress = 60
EX --> RT : 执行完成
RT --> GS : CommandResult.Succeeded\nprogress = 100

note right of GS
失败路径可替换终态为：
Failed / Cancelled / Expired
end note
@enduml
